The problem is that you assign your token in a different way.

When you do this `await asyncFunction();` Dart will wait till it is complete. But, when you do like this `asyncFunction().then((value) =&gt; print)` this tells Dart that it can continue executing your code, and when that asyncFunction is completed than print the value.

This is what happens on your case with

```dart
Candidate().getToken().then((value) {
      token = value;
    });
```

